title: Q&A at California Automobile Museum
description:
For this podcast Matt Farah goes to the California Autombobile Museum in Sacramento, CA, for a night of Q&A. Topics include Ferrari F40s, DeLoreans, starting TST, getting into video, and plenty more. 

Check out the list of cars and events at CA Auto Museum: 
www.calautomuseum.org
https://www.calautomuseum.org/exhibits-and-collections/current-vehicles/

This show is available as a video: https://youtu.be/UDPjwySTY5E


Follow us!
T: @thesmokingtire @zackklapman 
IG: @thesmokingtire @fakezackklapman 

Check out our merch!
https://teespring.com/stores/thesmokingtire?page=1
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
